//window.open case submit form, reload parent, and close child
-submit form, reload parent, and close child
- reload parent from childs submit
-   <button type="submit" id="form-btn" class="btn btn-success pull-right" onclick="doTheSubmit();">Send</button>
                      <input type="reset" class="btn btn-danger" value="Clear" />
                      <script type="text/javascript">
                      function doTheSubmit() {
                        window.opener.location.reload(); //reload parent windows
                      }
                      </script> it's from child form


- best answer:
 - add this to your ajax succes message area window.opener.location.reload(); if you want to load parent windows from child windows form submitted by ajax :)


